@prefix ex: <http://example.org/equality#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

ex:Marked a owl:Class .
ex:Chosen a owl:Class .

ex:Chosen owl:equivalentClass [
  a owl:Class ;
  owl:oneOf ( ex:anchor )
] .

ex:Marked rdfs:subClassOf ex:Chosen .
